TY  - JOUR
TI  - Systems k-Class Estimators
AU  - Savin, N. E.
AB  - [In this paper we generalize the family of single equation k-class estimators to systems of equations. The systems k-class estimator with k = 1 is the 3SLS estimator. After developing the asymptotic properties we introduce a further member of the systems k-class, the systems LVR estimator. A systems version of Basmann's identifiability test statistic is also considered.]
